AEW Dynamite Results 04-10-2024

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/746993f9-ee38-4c7f-b89c-33073a128f41/received_950185356604564.jpeg)

*   ## **_SAMOA JOE VS DUSTIN RHODES_**
    

The match does not happen as Swerve takes out Samoa Joe before he could finish his entrance as revenge for last week

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/223b03d8-3ee8-48da-bbe0-bd05639de665/20240410_171130.jpg)

*   ## **_TNT CHAMPIONSHIP OPEN CHALLENGE: ADAM COPELAND VS PENTA EL ZERO MIERDO_**
    

Copeland and Penta replace Joe and Distin to kick off the show. What a strange match. Nothing weird about it technically but just seeing Edge in the ring with Pentagon Jr. is WILD.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1a13e222-f75c-4db4-ae52-89c0a860b2b5/Screenshot_20240410_171934.jpg)

Midway through the match, the Bucks drop a countdown clock just like Cody's hilarious.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6a2a0500-c4a3-4280-8106-c1d91d605173/20240410_173235.jpg)

## **_WINNER: ADAM COPELAND_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5ede149b-b059-46c2-b955-6e12d8cebd8c/20240410_173742.jpg)

Julia Hart and Brody King attack Adam Copeland before Willow comes out, takes out Julia and distracts Brody enough for Adam to take him out

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f7a80c01-dd17-48aa-914a-fee6c191ec10/received_397026159793641.jpeg)

Someone once said “if you had a problem with Jack Perry, you got a problem with me.”

The Bucks begin to blame FTR for CM Punk's outbursts and Matt tells Nick he can’t just go around spreading rumors about people.

The Bucks say “after the incident” they needed to get their minds back together. They say they only reason they lost to FTR is because of CM Punk's incident with Jack Perry.

Bucks say the incident was short, like a high school scrap.

They play the footage and it confirms Punk was the aggressor. It also confirms CM Punk lunged at Tony Khan, knocking down monitors around him. Samoa Joe, Chris Hero, Ace Steel and Malakai Black take Punk away.

The Bucks come back and they reiterate they lost to FTR because of this distraction.

FTR comes to the ring for a semi-shoot promo where they say they want to move on from this incident 8 months ago.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/541347cc-919b-41a5-b2d9-bfcc1b8d7be0/20240410_180119.jpg)

Ospreay comes out to adress comments that “he isn’t about the grind” from a person who got their job grinding on the lap of their boss's daughter.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8c688c95-6826-45ae-8087-cac3313aaf45/Screenshot_20240410_182330.jpg)

